Text: RE Medicine Bow TieIn Capacity Cc Original Message From Lobban Laine Sent Tuesday September PM To Cc Coombs Craig Zinko Don Price Tom Wood Sally Warhover Judy Saye Steven Dalene Scott Gerlich Peter Hutton Tarry Koerner Steve Tomlinson Robert T Harris Roland Cook Mark Palazzari Catherine Subject Medicine Bow TieIn Capacity Dear Medicine Bow Shipper We received FERC approval this morning for the second segment of the Medicine Bow Tiein Capacity MDthd The contract will become effective September Additional capacity is available if you are able to utilize it I am out of the office today but I can be reached on my cell phone I will be back in the office on Monday October Please call me to discuss or with any questions Laine Lobban This email and any files transmitted with it from the ElPaso Corporation are confidential and intended solely for the use of the individual or entity to whom they are addressed If you have received this email in error please notify the sender
